==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: nǚzĭ wú cái biàn shì dé

===Proverb===
'''[[女子]][[無]][[才]][[便]][[是]][[德]]'''

# A woman who lacks talent is virtuous; An old fashioned saying meaning that women should stay at home.

===Alternate forms===
[[女子无才便是德]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

